Tarita Teriipaia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tarita_Teriipaia 0 Tarita Teri'ipaia (born December 29, 1941) is a former French actress of French Polynesian and Chinese descent most famous for having been the third wife of actor Marlon Brando, whom she later divorced. For media and entertainment appearances and engagements she has usually been billed as Tarita.
